d="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="386.11" base="394.03" width="195.123" height="9">ァルの日にプンクルを倒し、フルミネゕとリュ゙の</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p270_s26724" id="p270_w31" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="252.79" y="387.883" base="394.03" width="4.5" height="8.1">2</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p270_s26725" id="p270_w32" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="258.79" y="386.11" base="394.03" width="113.67" height="9">日間昏睡し、今日メルの日に起</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="328.276" height="9.873" id="p270_t21" x="48.264" y="403.18"><TOKEN sid="p270_s26726" id="p270_w33" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="403.18" base="411.1" width="74.28" height="9">きたというわけか。</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p270_s26727" id="p270_w34" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="118.347" y="403.18" base="411.1" width="98.526" height="9">外を見るともう真っ暗だ。</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p270_s26728" id="p270_w35" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="212.676" y="403.18" base="411.1" width="25.32" height="9">時計は</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p270_s26729" id="p270_w36" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="239.23" y="404.953" base="411.1" width="4.5" height="8.1">7</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p270_s26730" id="p270_w37" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="245.23" y="403.18" base="411.1" width="131.31" height="9">時のヴゔルフゔントを指している。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="261.492" height="9" id="p270_t22" x="56.424" y="420.1"><TOKEN sid="p270_s26733" id="p270_w38" font-name="ipa